== 评价 ==
影片的评价褒贬不一，但大多数为积极的，有些评价赞赏曼奴拉·沃拉斯科和原版电影暗黑色调的回归。西班牙语网站ALT104给予电影混合评价，声称这部电影被证明是一部有价值的续集，但是一种结束系列的无力方式<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/film-review-rec-4-apocalypse-1201304738/|title=‘[REC] 4: Apocalypse’ Review: Spanish Horror Franchise Bounces Back - Variety|author=Dennis Harvey|work=Variety|accessdate=2015-04-24|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027220035/https://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/film-review-rec-4-apocalypse-1201304738/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3312054/tiff-14-review-dull-pointless-rec-4-huge-disappointment/|title=[TIFF '14 Review] Dull and Pointless '[REC]4' Is a HUGE Letdown -|work=bloody-disgusting.com|accessdate=2015-04-24|archive-date=2015-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509012808/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3312054/tiff-14-review-dull-pointless-rec-4-huge-disappointment/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://alt1040.com/analisis/rec-4-apocalipsis|title=REC 4: Apocalipsis|work=Hipertextual|accessdate=2015-04-24|archive-date=2014-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102155306/http://alt1040.com/analisis/rec-4-apocalipsis|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

